# AI Gateway v2.0 - Quick Reference

## Endpoint Patterns

### ✅ CORRECT: Generic Endpoints

```bash
# Chat (all providers)
POST /api/v1/chat/completions
Body: { "model": "gpt-4|claude-4-sonnet|gemini-2.0|o1-preview", ... }

# Images (all providers)
POST /api/v1/images/generate
Body: { "model": "dall-e-3|imagen-3|sdxl-1.0", ... }

# MCP/External Tools (all providers)
POST /api/v1/mcp/:provider/:action
Example: /api/v1/mcp/tavily/search
```

### ❌ FORBIDDEN: Provider-Specific Endpoints

```bash
# DO NOT CREATE THESE
POST /api/v1/openai/chat
POST /api/v1/anthropic/chat
POST /api/v1/tavily/search      # Use /api/v1/mcp/tavily/search
```

## Model Detection

```javascript
// OpenAI
gpt-4, gpt-4-turbo, gpt-4o, gpt-3.5-turbo
o1-preview, o1-mini             // Deep research
dall-e-2, dall-e-3              // Images
whisper-1, tts-1                // Audio

// Anthropic
claude-4-sonnet, claude-3-5-sonnet, claude-3-haiku

// Google
gemini-2.0-flash, gemini-1.5-pro
imagen-3                        // Images
textembedding-gecko             // Embeddings

// Stability AI
sdxl-1.0, sd-3.5-large, sd-ultra

// Ollama (Local)
llama3, mistral, mixtral, codellama
```

## Adding New Capability

### LLM Capability (Model-Based)

1. Create generic endpoint: `/api/v1/{capability}/{action}`
2. Add provider detection logic
3. Implement provider-specific routing
4. Update documentation

### External Tool (Config-Based)

1. Add to `mcp-providers-config.json`:
```json
{
  "provider-name": {
    "baseUrl": "https://api.provider.com",
    "actions": {
      "action-name": {
        "path": "/action",
        "method": "POST",
        "auth": "bearer"
      }
    },
    "keyProvider": "provider-key-name"
  }
}
```
2. Use generic MCP proxy (no code changes!)

## Quick Checks

**Before creating new endpoint:**
- [ ] Is this an LLM capability? → Use model-based routing
- [ ] Is this an external tool? → Use MCP proxy
- [ ] Does similar endpoint exist? → Extend existing
- [ ] Will this scale to 100+ providers? → If no, redesign

**Documentation updates:**
- [ ] Updated GLOBAL_RULES_V3.md
- [ ] Updated ENDPOINT_ARCHITECTURE.md  
- [ ] Updated AIHDS_SERVICE_DISCOVERY_STANDARD.md
- [ ] Created/updated memory

## Common Mistakes

❌ Creating `/api/v1/openai/images`  
✅ Use `/api/v1/images/generate` with model parameter

❌ Creating `/api/v1/tavily/search`  
✅ Use `/api/v1/mcp/tavily/search`

❌ Hardcoding provider URLs  
✅ Use configuration files

❌ Hardcoding API keys  
✅ Fetch from AI Inferencing service

